### 기본 주소
@host = http://localhost:8080

### Spring Security 기본 계정
@username = user
@password = 05f9efe7-2940-4024-934c-efe49f7ceac2

### 테스트용 ID
@courseId = 2
@lectureId = 1

### 1. 특정 강좌의 강의 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}/lectures
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}



### 2. 강의 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}/lectures
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "title": "Java 1강",
  "description": "Java 기본 문법을 학습하는 강의입니다.",
  "videoUrl": "java-1.mp4",
  "thumbnailUrl": "java-1.png",
  "lectureOrder": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}


### 3. 강의 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lectures/{{lectureId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### 4. 강의 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lectures/{{lectureId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "title": "수정된 Java 1강",
  "description": "수정된 강의 설명입니다.",
  "videoUrl": "updated-java-1.mp4",
  "thumbnailUrl": "updated-java-1.png",
  "lectureOrder": 1,
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}


### 5. 강의 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lectures/{{lectureId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### 6. 삭제된 강의 상세 조회 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lectures/{{lectureId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}